    "Title": "Orange Lvl. Contract: Defend ~mission(Objects)",
    "Description": "I'm hoping that you'll be able to provide protection services at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>. One of our high priority clients is having some real trouble with a band of outlaws targeting their ~mission(Objects). Need to be able to keep the assets as safe and intact as possible. Client\u2019s expecting the service they pay for, so don\u2019t mess this up or we might lose a loyal customer.\n\nFor now, we\u2019re still a little in the dark when it comes to these outlaws, but if you manage to nail this to the Foxwell standards, we\u2019re offering  <EM4>~mission(ScripAmount) MG Scrip</EM4> to the main contractor. \n\nGood luck,\n\nKevin Walton\nDispatcher, Foxwell Enforcement\n'Security, Your Way'\n\nFoxwell Enforcement is a bonded security specialist licensed to operate throughout the UEE. We are always looking for new operators to join our family. If you or anyone you know is interested, please reach out to one of our contract representatives.",
